## Project Structure

Kale is a Next.js application built with React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.

### Key Entry Points

- [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - Main landing page
- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - Root layout component
- [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css) - Global styles
- [app/login/page.tsx](mdc:app/login/page.tsx) - Login page

### Component Organization

The components are organized by domain:
- `app/components/` - Root component directory
- `app/components/product/` - Product-related components
- `app/components/home/` - Home page components
- `app/components/search/` - Search functionality components
- `app/components/auth/` - Authentication components
- `app/components/layout/` - Layout components
- `app/components/ui/` - Reusable UI components

